snippet.title: Wulverblade PS4 - XBOX - Steam - Release Date
snippet.description:
Hey Everyone!

Finally after 6 long years we can announce the official release date for the PS4, XBOX and Steam versions for Wulverblade...and its NEXT WEEK! That's right, NEXT WEEK!

January 30th - 
Playstation 4 - https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/wulverblade-ps4/
Steam - http://store.steampowered.com/app/587180/Wulverblade/

January 31st
Xbox One - https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/p/wulverblade/c0vt6528fz91

We can't wait to get this into your hands. You've been so patient over the years and we really, really appreciate all the support! You all rock. Shares and likes are much appreciated!
